The library provides the following functions:

to initialize internal library structures
void init();

to cleanup internal library structures
void deinit();

clearing all strings in the http header
void clear_http_headers();

adds a string to the http header
int_http_header(const char*);

sends an http request and retrieves statistics after it has been executed
int perform_http_request(struct http_request_result * _http_request_result);